extendedInfo.description: TamiyaUSA's part support app gives R/Cr's the power of our website in the palm of their hands. Whether you are at the track or your workbench, you can research those parts you need. Keep up to date with our Facebook, Twitter and Youtube pages.

reviews.title: No TRF buggy\'s????
reviews.comment: Were are all the TRF buggy\'s???  Please update asap Thanx
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Total waste of time
reviews.comment: Doesn\'t know anything about the XV-01 which has been out for months. What\'s the point of a parts app that is never updated with new parts?  Update: The reply from the developer is simply wrong. XV-01 parts had been listed on Tamiya USA\'s site / store for months, but none were listed by the app. I reiterate, an app which lags both retail and Tamiya\'s site by months is essentially useless.  I note also that they took more than six months to bother replying, which shows how little effort is being put into the app.
reviews.author: Michael T.
